# Security Accepted-Risk Registry
#
# Format: GHSA_ID  WORKSPACE  DATE  REASON
# One entry per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Workspace: api | admin-web | mobile-pwa | packages | all
#
# An advisory listed here is ACCEPTED RISK — it will not fail security-audit.sh.
# All accepted risks must have a corresponding entry in docs/SECURITY_REVIEW_LOG.md.
#
# ── HOW TO ADD A NEW ENTRY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Understand the vulnerability and confirm it is not reachable in production.
# 2. Add the entry below with a clear reason.
# 3. Add a full accepted-risk entry in docs/SECURITY_REVIEW_LOG.md.
# 4. Get user approval before committing.
#
# ── REVIEW SCHEDULE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Review all accepted risks whenever the relevant package has a safe patch
# available, or at minimum once per milestone.
#
